			<div class="content" id="post-content-1841637">
									

<blockquote>
<p>Explained — A sub-class of object that has either been debunked as a hoax, sufficiently understood so as to be normal scientific knowledge, or so widely disseminated that containment is no longer possible.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>so widely disseminated that containment is no longer possible</p>
</blockquote>
<p>That's not &quot;explained,&quot; that's &quot;uncontained.&quot;</p>

